3. Majeed, Abdul (A.K.A. Majeed Chaudhry Abdul; A.K.A. Majid, Abdul) (date of birth: 15 April 1939; alternative date of birth: 1938; Nationality: Pakistani);
4. Tufail, Mohammed (A.K.A. Tufail, S.M.; A.K.A. Tufail, Sheik Mohammed) (Nationality: Pakistani).
